item.title: CVE-2020-36526|2024-08-04T17:30:08.095Z -- unspecified -- countdown%20timer
item.description: A vulnerability classified as problematic was found in Countdown Timer. This vulnerability affects unknown code of the component Macro Handler. The manipulation leads to cross site scripting. The attack can be initiated remotely. The exploit has been disclosed to the public and may be used.
